Hong Yan

Research Assistant Professor

Hong Kong Baptist University

Biography 🧚‍♀️

Dr. Hong YAN is a Research Assistant Professor at State Key Laboratory of Environmental and Biological Analysis (SKLEBA), Hong Kong Baptist University (HKBU). Her research interests are Tumor Metabolomics and Multi-Omics Network Analysis, specifically focusing on:

  1. Colorectal Cancer metabolomic reprogramming,
  2. Ferroptosis and KRAS mutations 🧬,
  3. Precision Medicine and Drug Repurposing 💊,
  4. Bioinformatics and data mining.
